snippet.title: Entanglement by Gopherwood Studios
snippet.description:
Entanglement by Gopherwood Studios
http://entanglement.gopherwoodstudios.com

Can YOU untangle the mystery of entanglement?

Entanglement is a new meditative puzzle game that challenges players to create the longest path possible.

Rotate and place tiles to form paths and create a most twisted tangle.

The longer your path grows in a single turn, the more points you earn!

Play to challenge yourself and others and you'll find yourself entangled in the possibilities.
